MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 616

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF LAURETA ELEMENTARY SCHOOL A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN SAN MIGUEL, TAGUM CITY, DAVAO DEL NORTE

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from the sale, entry, disposition or settlement and reserved for school site purposes of Laureta Elementary School under the administration of the Department of Education, a certain parcel of land of the public domain subject to final ground survey situated in San Miguel, Tagum City, Province of Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao, which is more particularly described as follows:

Lot No. 18, Csd-6510

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 18, Csd-6510) situated in San Miguel, Tagum City, Province of Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the Southeast, along lines 2-3-4-5-6 by Road; Southwest, along line 6-7 by Lot 19, Csd-6510; Northwest; along lines 7-8-9 by Road, along lines 9-10-11 by Lot 15, Csd-6510 along line 11-1 by Road; and along line 1-2 by Lot 17, Csd-6510. Beginning from point marked “1” on plan, being S. 84-06′ W., 2301.48 m. from B.L.L.M. No. 20, Cad-276. Thence:

153.64 m. to point 2;

162.34 m. to point 3;

5.33 m. to point 4;

73.73 m. to point 5;

193.42 m. to point 6;

116.74 m. to point 7;

135.39 m. to point 8;

8.50 m. to point 9;

43.87 m. to point 10;

37.04 m. to point 11;

8.29 m. to point of;

beginning, containing an area of FORTY TWO THOUSAND SEVEN HUNDRED FORTY FIVE (42,745) SQUARE METERS, more or less . All corners are P.S. Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cm. Bearings, True; Date of Original Survey, April 1935 to May 1938; Date of Subdivision Survey, August 4 to September 2, 1961; Surveyed by Geodetic Engineer Antonio Hernandez and approved on November 9, 1961.

The tracts of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease or other disposition until again declared alienable thru proclamation by the President.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 21st day of April, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

